mdui:UIInfo.mdui:Description: The Test Service Provider allows you to log into your home organisation, and to see what personal information they provide about you.
Die Toets Diens-Verskaffer laat u toe om by u tuis organisasie in te teken én om u persoonlike informasie te kontroleer wat hulle oor u verskaf.

Umhlinzeki Wesevisi Yokuhlola ukuvumela ukuthi ungene enhlanganweni yakho yasekhaya, futhi ubone ukuthi yiluphi ulwazi lomuntu siqu abalunikezayo olumayelana nawe. Ingabonisa zonke izici ezisekelwa yi-SAFIRE.
Umboneleli Wenkonzo Yovavanyo ukuvumela ungene kumbutho wakho wekhaya, uze ubone inkcazelp yobuqu abayinikeleyo ngawe. Ingabonisa zonke iimpawu ezixhaswa yi-SAFIRE.
